<div class="grid-container">
	<div class="p-t-large p-b-large lg-p-large pull-up--container container white shadow p-l-tiny p-r-tiny">
		<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
			<div class="small-12  cell">
				<h1 class="page-title">Reasons to Choose The Royal</h1>
			</div>
					</div>
		<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">

			
			<div class="small-12 cell">

			
				
				
						<!-- <p>Format of fields is <i>Title (type): 'field_name' - <strong>output</strong></i></p> -->
	
			

	<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x">
		<div class="small-12 cell">
			
			    
			    	<div class="container-fluid p-t-small p-b-small">
						<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x align-middle">

					    	
							
							 
						        <div class="small-12 medium-5 cell small-order-1 p-b-small md-p-b-none">

						        	
									<img title="Bath_UK" alt="" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415im_/https://3e6yx6lg8vw2h5wvv2le8ajf-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Bath_UK-467x350.jpg"/>
						        </div>

					         
						        <div class="small-12 medium-7 cell small-order-2">
						        	<h4><strong><b>LOCATION</b></strong><strong><b>, LOCATION, LOCATION</b></strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>Glorious Bath &#8230;&#8230;.. England&#8217;s only UNESCO World Heritage city, full of history, culture and atmosphere</li>
<li>Centrally located for all of the city&#8217;s wonderful attractions and the Thermae Spa, together with lots of scenic walks nearby</li>
<li>Convenient for rail travellers, being directly opposite Bath Spa station</li>
<li>Our hotel has limited car parking facilities, however there are almost 1000 covered, reasonably priced car parking spaces within a 2 minute walk</li>
</ul>

						        							        </div>

					    </div>

					</div>

			    
			    	<div class="container-fluid p-t-small p-b-small">
						<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x align-middle">

					    	
							
							 
						        <div class="small-12 medium-5 cell small-order-1 medium-order-2 p-b-small md-p-b-none">

						        	
									<img title="Royal0003" alt="" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415im_/https://3e6yx6lg8vw2h5wvv2le8ajf-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Royal0003-526x350.jpg"/>
						        </div>

					         
						        <div class="small-12 medium-7 cell small-order-2 medium-order-1">
						        	<h4><strong><b>INDEPENDENT AND PERSONAL<br/>
</b></strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>We are proudly independent, with the same owners for over 25 years, and the same manager for 15 years</li>
<li>We are not a &#8216;brand&#8217;, everything is personally tailored to create a high level of guest satisfaction</li>
<li>Each of our bedrooms is individually decorated in a style in keeping with the character of the hotel</li>
<li>Many of our wonderful staff have worked for us for a number of years, which helps to ensure a more friendly and personal service</li>
<li>We are a small intimate hotel, which radiates a warm &#8216;home from home&#8217; atmosphere</li>
<li>Please see the many complimentary reviews on Tripadvisor regarding our friendly staff</li>
</ul>

						        							        </div>

					    </div>

					</div>

			    
			    	<div class="container-fluid p-t-small p-b-small">
						<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x align-middle">

					    	
							
							 
						        <div class="small-12 medium-5 cell small-order-1 p-b-small md-p-b-none">

						        	
									<img title="Day Front Full – cropped and resized" alt="" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415im_/https://3e6yx6lg8vw2h5wvv2le8ajf-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Day-Front-Full-cropped-and-resized-468x350.jpg"/>
						        </div>

					         
						        <div class="small-12 medium-7 cell small-order-2">
						        	<h4><strong><b>CHARACTER AND CHARM</b></strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>The Royal is a lovely Grade2 listed building, designed by the renowned Isambard Kingdom Brunel, and first opened in 1846 &#8211; over 170 years of history and hospitality</li>
<li>The decor throughout is warm and hospitable</li>
<li>Our restaurant is designed in the charming style of a Parisian brasserie, as opposed to a typical hotel dining room</li>
</ul>

						        							        </div>

					    </div>

					</div>

			    
			    	<div class="container-fluid p-t-small p-b-small">
						<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x align-middle">

					    	
							
							 
						        <div class="small-12 cell small-order-2">
						        	<h4><strong><b>COMFORT AND SAFETY</b></strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>You will enjoy the comfort of quality Egyptian cotton bed linen, feather filled duvets and pillows in all bedrooms</li>
<li>Our four poster and superior rooms are also provided with cotton bathrobes and slippers</li>
<li>We have established a &#8220;safe haven&#8221; against COVID-19 with our Hygiene and Cleanliness Best Practices staff training programme, which fully complies with Government guidelines and more (details of which will be displayed for guests)</li>
</ul>

						        							        </div>

					    </div>

					</div>

			    
			    	<div class="container-fluid p-t-small p-b-small">
						<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x align-middle">

					    	
							
							 
						        <div class="small-12 medium-5 cell small-order-1 p-b-small md-p-b-none">

						        	
									<img title="thermae-bath-spa cropped" alt="" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415im_/https://3e6yx6lg8vw2h5wvv2le8ajf-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/thermae-bath-spa-cropped-398x350.jpg"/>
						        </div>

					         
						        <div class="small-12 medium-7 cell small-order-2">
						        	<h4><strong><b>QUALITY AND VALUE</b></strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>You will find in your bedroom a &#8216;hospitality tray&#8217; with complimentary cafetière ground coffee, a selection of teas, hot chocolate, mineral water and biscuits, all replenished daily during your stay.</li>
<li>Our award winning breakfast is included with all of our room rates.  Please view our excellent breakfast menu <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415/https://www.royalhotelbath.co.uk/breakfast-menu">here</a>, and the great reviews on Tripadvisor.</li>
<li>Unlike other hotels, when you dine on an inclusive dinner basis, you are offered the full à la carte menu selection to choose from &#8211; no set menu with restrictive choice when you dine with us!  Please have a look at the selection of dishes available <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415/https://www.royalhotelbath.co.uk/restaurant/brasserie-brunel-menu">here</a>, and again visit Tripadvisor to read the very complimentary reviews regarding our food.</li>
<li>We believe that we have the best value Spa Leisure Break available in Bath.  Please click <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415/https://www.royalhotelbath.co.uk/spa-breaks">here</a> for details.</li>
<li>When booking direct with us you will save at least 15% on current rates, plus gain other benefits compared to booking via another source, click <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220819012415/https://www.royalhotelbath.co.uk/special-offers/get-the-best-deal-by-booking-direct">here</a> for more details.</li>
<li>Become a Loyalty Card member (free to join) and enjoy fantastic savings. You will be rewarded with 10% off your total bill for all future stays. In addition, you will be offered exclusive special deals.</li>
</ul>

						        							        </div>

					    </div>

					</div>

			    
			    	<div class="container-fluid p-t-small p-b-small">
						<div class="grid-x grid-padding-x align-middle">

					    	
							
							 
						        <div class="small-12 cell small-order-2">
						        	<p><em><i>With everything that The Royal has to offer</i></em><em><i>,</i></em><em><i> we do hope that you will choose to stay with us for your next short break or when visiting Bath</i></em><em><i>,</i></em><em><i> and we very much look forward to welcoming you.</i></em></p>

						        							        </div>

					    </div>

					</div>

			    
					</div>
	</div>


	

								
	    	
				
						
