  <h1 class="entry-title single-title">Inclusive Mini Break from £169 pp</h1>
<section class="entry-content">
<ul>
<li>2 or 3 nights’ accommodation in a standard double or twin room.</li>
<li>A glass of refreshing Champagne pre-dinner each evening.</li>
<li>3 course dinner selected from the full à la carte menu each evening (no supplements).</li>
<li>Our award winning breakfast – a wide choice of healthy options, plus a cooked to order hot breakfast, including vegetarian dishes.</li>
<li>Complimentary ‘hospitality tray’ in your room, with cafetière ground coffee, a selection of teas, hot chocolate, biscuits and mineral water (all replenished daily).</li>
</ul>
<p>All from £169 pp (2 nights) and £249 pp (3 nights) Sun-Thurs, with a £50 pppn supplement Fri-Sat. Saving up to £80 per couple based on 2 persons sharing a double or twin standard room.</p>
<p>Please quote <strong>MINI BREAK</strong> when making your reservation.</p>
</section>
